<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَأَيْضًا مِنْ عَلامَتِهِ اهْتِمَامٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>بِهَمٍ وَاحِدٍ غَيْرَ انْتِحَالِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَيَصْرَفُ هَمَّهُ للهِ صِرْفًا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَيَتْرُكُ مَا سِوَاهُ مِنَ المَوَالِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَأَيْضًا مِنْ عَلامَتِهِ إِذَا مَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>دَنَا وَقْتُ الصَّلاةِ لِذِي الجَلالِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَأَحْرَمَ دَاخِلاً فِيهَا بِقَلْبٍ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>مُنِيبٍ خَاضِعٍ فِي كُلِّ حَالِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>تَنَاءَى هَمُّهُ وَالغَمُّ عَنْهُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>بِدُنْيَا تَضْمَحِلُّ إِلَى زَوَالِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَوَافَى رَاحَةٌ وَسُرُورَ قَلْبٍ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَقُرَّةَ عَيْنِهِ وَنَعِيمَ بَالِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَيَشْتَدُّ الخُرُوجُ عَلَيْهِ فِيهَا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فَيَرْغَبُ جَاهِدًا فِي الابْتِهَالِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَأَيْضًا مِنْ عَلامَتِهِ اهْتِمَامٌ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>بِتَصْحِيحِ المَقَالَةِ وَالفِعَالِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَأَعْمَالٍ وَنِيَّاتٍ وَقَصْدٍ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>عَلَى الإِخْلاصِ يَحرصُ بِالكَمَالِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
